  Lord Shen: “How did you find peace? I took away your parents,
         everything, I scarred you for life.”

  Kung Fu Panda: See that’s the thing Shen, scars heal,

  Shen: No they don’t… wounds heal.

  Panda: Oh yah… what do scars do? They fade I guess.

  Shen: I don’t care what scars do…

  Panda: “You should Shen.  You got to let go of the stuff from past –
        because it just doesn’t matter. The only thing that matters is what 
        you choose to be now.”

  Po: “Maybe I should just quit and go back to making noodles.”

  Oogway: “Quit, don’t quit? Noodles, don’t noodles? You are too concerned 
